&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank Staff Nurse and Operating Theatre Practitioner Band 5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Royal Wolverhampton NHS Trust is looking for newly qualified registered nurse / ODP or experienced theatre practitioners to join our dynamic and innovative theatre teams at Cannock Chase and New Cross Hospitals on our Bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Theatre Directorate covers a wide range of surgical specialties including Cardiothoracic, Day Case, Gynaecology (including robotic), General, Breast, Colo-rectal, Urology (including robotic), Head and Neck, Trauma and Orthopedics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joining our exceptional, committed, caring and compassionate teams as a theatre practitioner will allow you to provide high quality, efficient peri-operative care to all patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
